#: ../new/triggeractions.rst:4
msgid "Trigger Actions"
msgstr ""

#: ../new/triggeractions.rst:6
msgid ":game:`Ares` adds the following Trigger Actions to :game:`Yuri's Revenge`."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/triggeractions.rst:8
msgid ""
"See :doc:`Editor Support </new/editorsupport>` on how to use the new "
"Trigger Actions from map editors."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/triggeractions.rst:15
msgid ":captiontag:`Activate Firestorm` (92)"
msgstr ""

#: ../new/triggeractions.rst:17
msgid ""
"Activates the Firestorm Wall sections for the house owning the trigger, "
"regardless of charge state of the super weapon. The Firestorm will not "
"drain the charge, but it will shut down once the house loses power."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/triggeractions.rst:21 ../new/triggeractions.rst:38
msgid "These map action is only supported for non-human controlled houses."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/triggeractions.rst:23
msgid "The format is :value:`92,0,0,0,0,0,0,A`."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/triggeractions.rst:32
msgid ":captiontag:`Deactivate Firestorm` (93)"
msgstr ""

#: ../new/triggeractions.rst:34
msgid ""
"Dectivates the Firestorm Wall sections for the house owning the trigger. "
"Use this only to turn off a Firestorm that was activated using Trigger "
"Action :value:`92`."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/triggeractions.rst:40
msgid "The format is :value:`93,0,0,0,0,0,0,A`."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/triggeractions.rst:49
msgid ":captiontag:`Auxiliary Power` (146)"
msgstr ""

#: ../new/triggeractions.rst:51
msgid ""
"Permanently adds an amount to the specified house's auxiliary power. Can "
"be negative to create a drain or remove previously given auxiliary power."
" Applying this effect multiple times is cumulative."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/triggeractions.rst:55
msgid "The format is :value:`146,11,<house id>,0,0,0,0,<power>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/triggeractions.rst:64
msgid ":captiontag:`Kill Drivers Of` (147)"
msgstr ""

#: ../new/triggeractions.rst:66
msgid ""
"Kills all drivers of the units that have the trigger attached that "
"contains this action. This action respects Protected Drivers, Iron "
"Curtain and all the other mechanisms that prevent drivers being killed."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/triggeractions.rst:70
msgid ""
"All affected units will change to the country specified by the house "
"index. Use :value:`-1` to change the owner to the house called "
":value:`Special`."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/triggeractions.rst:73
msgid "The format is :value:`147,0,<house id>,0,0,0,0,A`."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/triggeractions.rst:82
msgid ":captiontag:`Set EVA Voice` (148)"
msgstr ""

#: ../new/triggeractions.rst:84
msgid ""
"Sets the player's EVA voice. The builtin EVAs are :value:`0`, :value:`1`,"
" and :value:`2` for Allied, Russian and Yuri respectively. Higher numbers"
" represent the custom EVAs. Use :value:`-1` to disable EVA."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/triggeractions.rst:88
msgid ""
"This implements the :game:`Firestorm` trigger actions :value:`Disable "
"EVA` (102) and :value:`Enable EVA` (103)."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/triggeractions.rst:91
msgid "The format is :value:`148,0,<eva index>,0,0,0,0,A`."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/triggeractions.rst:100
msgid ":captiontag:`Set Group` (149)"
msgstr ""

#: ../new/triggeractions.rst:102
msgid ""
"Sets the group number for the object that triggered this action. This can"
" be used to make units available for recruitment through "
":type:`TeamTypes` and :tag:`TaskForces`."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/triggeractions.rst:106
msgid ""
"This implements the :game:`Firestorm` trigger action :value:`Set Group` "
"(104)."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/triggeractions.rst:108
msgid "The format is :value:`149,0,<group number>,0,0,0,0,A`."
msgstr ""

